{
  "stem": "11552.5",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was very shortly, about maybe a month later-- it was in the month of November when the village was liberated by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was with the cows when one of the boys came and said, they're looking for you.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I say, who?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He says, the Russians.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he was so petrified.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He says, maybe you should hide.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I say, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "What happened-- oh, by the way, during that period of time I was in the village, one day I was out with the cows.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I saw a head going up and down the rows of the potatoes-- a straw head going down and pulling the potatoes.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I said to myself, who could be stealing potatoes?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Oh, Jews or partisans.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So after this head disappeared, I took all the potato stalks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I put them right back into the earth.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Because I was afraid, you know, the farmer sees somebody was stealing his potatoes, they would go to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And before you know it, it's trouble.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So I put them all back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Well, anyway, [LAUGHS] later on I found out it was one of the partisans stealing the potatoes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So-- So now talking about liberation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, so they, they asked me to go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I didn't make a fuss, because after all, the Russians are not going to kill me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They brought me to this school, the same school where, where they had this kitchen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I walked in there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was-- they were sitting there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, and this, this boy who brought-- this soldier who brought me there didn't have epaulets.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't know if he was an officer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was just wearing a regular Russian uniform.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they said, is this the girl, one of the high-ranking officer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he said, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
